Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:06.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio. This is a story from before you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A story up to when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:16.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your Mommy and Daddy first spoke to each other when we were seniors in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.58,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,That's when you first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:22.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. We didn't even know each other's name until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:31.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sweet bean bread! {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:43.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But nothing can stay unchanged. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fun things... Happy things... {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They can't all possibly stay unchanged. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, can you keep on loving this place? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just find them. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:21.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just find new fun and happy things. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's get going. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:14.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's how we got to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:19.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was a year older than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, how can I help you? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wanted to ask why you're eating lunch out here alone. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not particularly. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:45.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I used to have friends and teachers I got along with, but now... {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Did something happen? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:52.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Last year, I was away from school for a long period of time. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I'm... {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:54.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're repeating. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm repeating. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:07.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,All the people I knew graduated,\Nand only people I don't know fill the school. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I feel like Urashima Tarou. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.29,Note,,0,0,0,,Note: Urashima Tarou is a story in which the protagonist jumps forward in time and finds no one he knew alive. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.69,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Recap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.69,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Under the Green Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Daddy was an outcast at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:40.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But after meeting Mommy,\Nthings started to change little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was trying to get involved in theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:50.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But to do that, she first had to reestablish the Theater Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.46,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,You helped her do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:57.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mommy was so serious about it, I couldn't ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:06.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even then, Mommy loved the Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You love it, too, don't you, Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.98,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was practicing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She had a play she wanted to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,...would you like me to take you? {S1 ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:30.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To the place in this city where wishes come true. {S1 ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then started the gathering of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:39.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,First to join us was Fujibayashi Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know her. She's your teacher at kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.89,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You can't. {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:51.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm... how do I put it... not dating you or anything. {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Besides, Ryou would... {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Stop! {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:55.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Listen to me! {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:06:02.49,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Of course, you're a boy,\Nso I understand you have an interest in it... {S1 ep17}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then her younger sister, Fujibayashi Ryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She was Daddy's class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.96,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,O-Okay. I will listen to you seriously. {S1 ep4}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.71,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's starting to look more and more like a Theater Club. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:19.05,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,All girls like fortune-telling at the genetic level. {S1 ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The smartest girl in school joined us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ichinose Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She turned out to be a childhood friend of Daddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So nice. {S1 ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There were many others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like Sakagami Tomoyo from the junior class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.86,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The path we are taking is still continuing. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.07,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Let us both keep working hard. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.49,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's a promise. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sagara Misae-san, the dorm parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:53.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Also, Miyazawa Yukine, who was always in the Reference Room to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa taught me the legend that's told in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"An orb of light appears to those who are happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She says that getting hold of those will grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.43,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,How about Youhei Oji-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh right, forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is the game in the name of love guys play. {S2 ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.25,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a boy love game. {S2 ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:28.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I once worked with Mei-chan, his younger sister, to get him back on the soccer club, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:35.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If he hadn't been there, I probably would have dropped out of school before I met Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:47.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We all went to different places,\Nbut we still get together from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They all came to our place last New Year's,\Nso you remember them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Many things happened before\Nthe Theater Club was reestablished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:04.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,For example, Yoshino Yusuke-san and Kouko-san's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kouko-san had a sister who was in hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That'd be your friend, Fuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:20.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Other than members, we had to find a teacher who would watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:24.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There was a fight over Koumura-sensei with the Choir,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and we even challenged\Nthe basketball team to convince the Choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In the end, Kyou, Sunohara,\Nand everyone else joined the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:41.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The Theater Club finally started to move thanks to the work of many people, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:46.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...after that, trouble emerged for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pops, if you're going to sleep, you should lie down. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.26,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, hi. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:59.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I guess I caused Tomoya-kun some trouble again. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:05.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Back then, Daddy wasn't getting along with Daddy's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I left home and decided to live at Mommy's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Father. {S1 ep19}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.02,San,San,0,0,0,,So my... my bread is... {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,H-Hey. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.73,San,San,0,0,0,,It was natural there would be leftovers?! {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:29.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like mother, like daughter. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hope the father is sane. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You said what you're not supposed to say. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't need to hear about Sanae-san and Akki, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:46.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There was a time when we all played baseball at Akki's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:53.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Both Sanae-san and Akki welcomed me into their home kindly from the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:10:01.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wasn't too sure what a family was like,\Nso I was lost in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:06.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But Sanae-san and Akki were both looking after me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was physically weak,\Nso sometimes she'd be in bed, sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:18.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san and Akki took great care of Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The truth is always harsh. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The School Festival was coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:33.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We started to work hard for our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But something came up at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,These pictures... {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I found old albums and diaries. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, I never knew about this. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I never knew Dad used to act. {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:01.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And yet... they both gave up their dreams for me... {S1 ep21}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This isn't good! Let's drop the curtain. {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:23.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Make your dream come true, Nagisa!!! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What? {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:26.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man? {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot or what?! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.74,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A child's dream is their parents' dream! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So you grant it for us! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:39.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We've been dreaming of the day you would make your dream come true! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:42.24,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We didn't give up our dreams! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We changed our dreams to your dream! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what parents are! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.13,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what family is!!! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So... ever since that day... {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Every day, while baking bread... {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:00.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,...we've been living, waiting for this day! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If you fail here, we'll be depressed! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:08.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You've got a huge responsibility on your back, you hear me?! {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shall I... {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shall I take you? {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To the place in this city where wishes come true? {ep1}{S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Take us there, Nagisa. {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take us away. {S1 ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The play ended as a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.66,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,What was the story about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A story of a girl who lived in a world that had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We didn't know the title or the author of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The ending of the story was a mystery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:06.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy said it might be something she heard from someone when she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:12.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But strangely, it felt like I knew the story, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:24.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then Mommy and Daddy promised to keep walking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right before graduation, a major problem arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy became ill and couldn't graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was really shocked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I should have repeated, too, after all. {S2 ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. {S2 ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:06.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't stop like that. {S2 ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you can move on, then you should. {S2 ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please move on. {S2 ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After graduation, I helped\NSanae-san and Akki for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I knew I couldn't do that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:55.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So I asked Yoshino-san and got work at an electrical company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Obviously, I only made mistakes in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I might have given up if it had been the me from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:13.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I managed to keep with it thanks to\NMommy's support and coworkers helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy did her best to keep going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:29.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At that time, there was a chance for\NDaddy to transfer to a bigger company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But due to various issues, it fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:44.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Again, Mommy was the person who supported me when I was about to give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was when I proposed to Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I couldn't get married right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:16:01.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy got ill again and couldn't go to her graduation after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:10.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But for Mommy's sake, everyone gathered and held a graduation for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:15.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Daddy and Mommy got married right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:24.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We became husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:27.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then in Mommy's tummy, a baby came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was you, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.78,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But Mommy wasn't strong physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was a big hassle until you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:50.76,San,San,0,0,0,,I was told by the doctor that there will be some danger during the delivery. {S2 ep15}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.06,San,San,0,0,0,,I have not told this to Nagisa yet. {S2 ep15}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.68,San,San,0,0,0,,Only I've been told. {S2 ep15}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:03.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When I was getting crushed from the anxiety,\NAkki told me an old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:08.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The trees and bushes enveloped the sick Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:13.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Before he noticed it, Mommy was returned to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A story like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio? Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did she fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have a strange memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:34.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I haven't told Ushio yet, but she was born once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:41.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In that memory, Nagisa died when Ushio was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:56.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I left Ushio in the care of the Furukawas and lived alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then, during the summer Ushio was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:13.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We went on a trip just like Sanae-san had planned, and at the final destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Grandmother told me many stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:29.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just as I told many stories right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was a story from before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:43.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right now, Pops is back at his mother's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:48.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm planning to go see him in the near future with Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:56.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So we started living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio's teacher at the kindergarten was Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio became friends with Fuko, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everything was going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Until...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ushio? {S2 ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:21.43,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I couldn't pee alone. {S2 ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ushio?! {S2 ep20}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It felt like I was having a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course, Ushio beside me is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's never caught any major illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:49.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But Ushio in that world never recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At that moment, something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When I came to, Nagisa was right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was back to five years ago, the day Ushio was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's such a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:46.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I think it's something that really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa and I met in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and Ushio was born in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I met many people in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:14.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and I lived through many things in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:21.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll continue to live, being supported by many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll catch colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's about time you both wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:57.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shio-chan! Daddy! Fu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:01.67,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Mommy!
